trans-unit.source: The ConfigurationSet class represents a configuration set for one or more AD LDS instances.
trans-unit.target: ConfigurationSet 類別表示組態集內的一或多個 AD LDS 執行個體。

trans-unit.source: Gets a read-only collection of AD LDS instances that are in the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 取得唯讀集合的 AD LDS 組態中設定的執行個體。

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection"></xref> object that contains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance"></xref> objects that are in the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstanceCollection"> </xref>物件，其中包含<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.AdamInstance"></xref>組態中設定的物件。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已處置。

trans-unit.source: The object has been disposed.
trans-unit.target: 物件已處置。

trans-unit.source: Releases all managed and unmanaged resources that are used by the object.
trans-unit.target: 釋放物件所使用的所有 managed 和 unmanaged 資源。

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources that are used by the object and optionally releases managed resources.
trans-unit.target: 釋放物件所使用的 unmanaged 的資源並選擇性釋放 managed 的資源。

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Boolean> value that determines if the managed resources should be released.
trans-unit.target: A<xref:System.Boolean>值，決定是否應該釋出 managed 的資源。</xref:System.Boolean>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the managed resources should be released; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if only the unmanaged resources should be released.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果應該釋放 managed 的資源。<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>如果只釋出 unmanaged 的資源。

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext"></xref> object that contains the target and credentials to use to retrieve the object.
trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.DirectoryContext"> </xref>物件，其中包含的目標和認證来用來擷取物件。

trans-unit.source: The target of the context can be an AD LDS instance or keywords that are specified in the serviceConnectionPoint object in the current forest that can identify the configuration set.
trans-unit.target: 此內容的目標可以是 AD LDS 執行個體或指定 serviceConnectionPoint 物件中可以識別組態集的目前樹系中的關鍵字。

trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ConfigurationSet"> </xref>物件，代表組態集為指定的內容。
